71
00:05:21.790 --> 00:05:23.980
It’s not a large sum of money to me. 

72
00:05:23.980 --> 00:05:26.940
And, it’s not to a stranger. Now, we are all Avengers Club members

73
00:05:26.940 --> 00:05:28.640
and we agreed to seek 
revenge together.

74
00:05:36.840 --> 00:05:38.280
Okay, then.

75
00:05:38.430 --> 00:05:39.880
Let’s be frank.

76
00:05:40.940 --> 00:05:49.520
I did come here because I was furious, but I don’t think I can trust the two of you yet.

77
00:05:49.620 --> 00:05:51.730
