81
00:06:02.600 --> 00:06:05.260
I… I am not.

82
00:06:05.260 --> 00:06:07.050
Yes, you look that way.

83
00:06:07.050 --> 00:06:11.130
What in the world is the problem? 
You need money immediately after all.

84
00:06:11.310 --> 00:06:13.230
Since I have it, I’m just saying 
that I’ll give it to you is all.

85
00:06:13.230 --> 00:06:16.910
Look here. Starting the other day, you keep treating me like a beggar…

86
00:06:16.910 --> 00:06:21.410
