107
00:07:52.360 --> 00:07:54.810
It was a marriage to connect 
two families.

108
00:07:56.170 --> 00:07:58.940
How great a family do you belong to that you can’t even get a divorce.

109
00:07:59.180 --> 00:08:02.570
HaeRan Construction. 
And, my family is GeoNa.

110
